      <prefercite id="aspace_68ac455b6e44da6f72a3bae2fe2c6652">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Collection of Bookplates by Adri de Ruijter, Robert B. Haas Family Arts Library, Yale University.</p>  
